import { Grid } from '@material-ui/core'
import React from 'react'

interface IProps{
    isReadOnly: boolean
}

const MenuLayout: React.FC<IProps> = (props) => {

    return(
        <Grid
            spacing={2}
            container>
            <Grid
                item
                xs={12}>

            </Grid>
            <Grid
                container>
                <Grid item>

                </Grid>
                <Grid item>
                    
                </Grid>
            </Grid>
        </Grid>
    )
}

export default MenuLayout
